data.description: This lovely 2 story home is situated in the desirable neighborhood of The Willows in Henderson, Nevada. Featuring 3 bedrooms and a loft, this home provides ample space and flexibility for various lifestyles. This well maintained home features a open living to kitchen, with a pantry, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, landscaped backyard with a large patio and patio cover. A/C condensor replaced in 2022 with warranty.  Downstairs has beautiful laminate flooring, large upstair laundry rm, carpet upstairs. Primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower, large walk in closet. This property offers close proximity to the 95 freeway, Costco, Cowabunga Bay, The galleria Mall, Henderson Hospital and so much more.
